Reimbursement
code it Wright








Home › Reimbursement 










Code It Wright is designed to provide coding, coverage and reimbursement information to both our internal and external customers. Code It Wright is intended for those involved in the coding and reporting of provider services. Our customers are able to access information regarding coding and reimbursement of services and obtain an understanding of how Wright products can fit into healthcare coding and reimbursement reporting.
Cannot find information for a specific product? Please click the “C code” link to the right or click located here.
For further reimbursement questions, please contact your current local sales representative, or submit
additional questions to Code It Wright.




