Why Wright
We care about what we do and how we do it. At Wright we strive to create a working environment that fosters ingenuity, teamwork and a commitment to the highest standards of ethical conduct. We recognize our success has been built upon the dedication of our team members and we provide the opportunity to develop careers based on individual strengths and potential.
We are always looking for people who share our passion and sense of purpose. Career opportunities at Wright give you the chance to find an new challenge, discover the best in yourself, and grow along with the premier global, orthopedic extremities—biologics company. If you want to make a difference, then we want to hear from you.
Wright Medical Group N.V. through its direct and indirect affiliates and subsidiaries (“Wright”) has been and will continue to be an equal opportunity employer. To assure full implementation of this equal employment policy, Wright will take steps to assure that persons are recruited, hired, assigned and promoted without regard to race, religion, color, national origin, citizenship, sex, veteran’s status, age, disability or any other legally protected status. EOE M/F/D/V












Why I Work at Wright





Bruce, Finance Manager
“Every part of the business is impacted by financial information. If we don’t make money, we can’t continue to operate. It’s fun to take expertise in finance and accounting and model scenarios to see how each scenario turns into profit and cash for our company to continue to grow”


Watch The Video












Buck, Machinist III
“People want to learn their responsibility and become really good at it. It is natural to resist change. But we are constantly changing. We have to adapt. The machinery changes and the products change. There is change every day. We have to be able to change!”


Watch The Video












Imogen, International MarCom Representative
“It’s a great working environment. I really enjoy working here. There have been a lot of changes, even in my short time at Wright, but that is what I like about the position. Every day is different. It changes all the time and I don’t get bored!”


Watch The Video












Sandy, Senior Returns Coordinator
“Wright operates with a high level of integrity, realizing its employees are its most valuable resource, and investing in and developing us to reach our highest potential! Our work environment is open, friendly, fun and employees have a sense of freedom in performing their jobs. Wright demonstrates a genuine concern for employees, community, and our families. It’s a great place to work!”


Watch The Video










